      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, it is in truly stunning shape! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014super clean, meticulously cared for, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s ready for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as appreciated. You\u2019ve really got to see this one in person to believe how gorgeous it is. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
