    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a showroom-spec E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to achieve a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This chassis is structurally impeccable, with documented subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing prophylaxis. The exterior maintains its factory-original luster with zero imperfections, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. Mechanically optimized with a fresh valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul, this is a turnkey investment for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
